{"tid":1041254,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"到底jojo點解會有咁多死忠(打手)？","createTime":"2019-02-28T16:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T20:56:55.000Z","uid":15842,"like":25,"dislike":221,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c67d3a64501b155f987aa4cc44e54bc1d3d2f2","tid":1041254,"uid":15842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"讚到天上有地下無不特止 一有人批評下就十幾廿條友負皮落人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底套野有乜咁特別？打架鬥智動畫大把啦老實講 啲畫風又難頂 角色啲舉止表情又九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇到第三個jojo一半都已經頂唔順棄咗 得2jo係中後段開始叫幾好睇幾感人 第三已經係每一集循環咁出新敵人-&gt;主角團有危機-&gt;解決危機 又唔係真係好緊湊 明明成日搞啲笑位但套野又唔似想做笑片個類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底點解會有咁多人擁護呢套野？"},{"pid":"aad0a7d9b6ffa69a81815f4f7176e3dd13515a63","tid":1041254,"uid":72265,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"佢有啲位誇張得濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9c9526a76f90ed03e05a5860cdf36c2d59e965","tid":1041254,"uid":135053,"like":70,"dislike":5,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"因為好睇囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/01/004820_d92fb77bd5933803072c4093643c6db6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F01%2F004820_d92fb77bd5933803072c4093643c6db6.gif&h=3f7b1999&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d68093d008470552de3d7c9c74a2a729645be5a","tid":1041254,"uid":87132,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"百貨應百客啫<br />\n唔中意咪唔好睇囉 又無人逼你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e2c2eb5e6b0ea16bd9c8cccfb505127c6f8cf8","tid":1041254,"uid":15842,"like":7,"dislike":24,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"1d68093d008470552de3d7c9c74a2a729645be5a","tid":1041254,"uid":87132,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"reply